{"tid":1130232,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"15歲仔墮「執法人員」陷阱 變賣母25萬首飾匯款騙徒","createTime":"2019-04-29T01:44:36.000Z","updateTime":"2019-04-29T22:36:01.000Z","uid":130626,"like":12,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":16,"replies":[{"pid":"c9077c3cb711f9f4c0d83506a048678addb27f50","tid":1130232,"uid":130626,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-04-29T01:44:36.000Z","msg":"電騙黨又得逞！昨日(28日)晚上7時許，一名49歲女子在將軍澳廣明苑一單位報案，指失去一批首飾。警方接報到場調查，女事主15歲兒子指早前收到一名男子來電，對方自稱是內地執法人員，並指他涉及一宗刑事案件，少年按該名男子指示，將其母親約值25萬港元的首飾變賣，並將款項存入一內地戶口。<br />\n警方經初步調查，案件列作以欺騙手段取得財產，交由將軍澳警區刑事調查隊，暫未有人被捕。<br />\n<img src=\"https://s.yimg.com/ny/api/res/1.2/e99n9OK9dg03xca5kuy1Vw--~A/YXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM0/http://media.zenfs.com/en/homerun/feed_manager_auto_publish_494/ca8f15f75a2b6fe3adc57bbdd8f26458\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fs.yimg.com%2Fny%2Fapi%2Fres%2F1.2%2Fe99n9OK9dg03xca5kuy1Vw--~A%2FYXBwaWQ9aGlnaGxhbmRlcjtzbT0xO3c9NjA4O2g9NDM0%2Fhttp%3A%2F%2Fmedia.zenfs.com%2Fen%2Fhomerun%2Ffeed_manager_auto_publish_494%2Fca8f15f75a2b6fe3adc57bbdd8f26458&h=5a551448&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<a href=\"https://hk.news.yahoo.com/15%E6%AD%B2%E4%BB%94%E5%A2%AE%E3%80%8C%E5%9F%B7%E6%B3%95%E4%BA%BA%E5%93%A1%E3%80%8D%E9%99%B7%E9%98%B1%E3%80%80%E8%AE%8A%E8%B3%A3%E6%AF%8D25%E8%90%AC%E9%A6%96%E9%A3%BE%E5%8C%AF%E6%AC%BE%E9%A8%99-235611176.html\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.news.yahoo.com%2F15%25E6%25AD%25B2%25E4%25BB%2594%25E5%25A2%25AE%25E3%2580%258C%25E5%259F%25B7%25E6%25B3%2595%25E4%25BA%25BA%25E5%2593%25A1%25E3%2580%258D%25E9%2599%25B7%25E9%2598%25B1%25E3%2580%2580%25E8%25AE%258A%25E8%25B3%25A3%25E6%25AF%258D25%25E8%2590%25AC%25E9%25A6%2596%25E9%25A3%25BE%25E5%258C%25AF%25E6%25AC%25BE%25E9%25A8%2599-235611176.html&d=5ezJA%2FdytRM7iHrFGdkn9YuQyocENDzUuJTHoiHzCac%3D&h=280d4637\" target=\"_blank\">https://hk.news.yahoo.com/15%E6%AD%B2%E4%BB%94%E5%A2%AE%E3%80%8C%E5%9F%B7%E6%B3%95%E4%BA%BA%E5%93%A1%E3%80%8D%E9%99%B7%E9%98%B1%E3%80%80%E8%AE%8A%E